data.description: Welcome to this stunning two-story home nestled on a charming corner lot. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the grandeur of the cathedral ceilings and the inviting warmth of the gas fireplace, perfect for cozy gatherings during colder months. This property offers many updates, including a brand NEW water heater! With four spacious bedrooms, including a main floor master ensuite, this home offers flexibility and comfort for your family's needs. The heart of this home is the updated kitchen, featuring a brand NEW dishwasher, ensuring clean up is a breeze. The dining room has been enhanced with NEW lighting, creating a delightful atmosphere for family dinners and entertaining guests. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the home, only a few years old, offers both durability and style, making cleaning a cinch and adding a contemporary touch. A fenced-in yard adds an element of privacy and security, making it ideal for outdoor activities and pets. Plus, the entire home has been freshly painted, giving it a crisp and clean appearance. Conveniently located near local schools, shopping, and just minutes away from Interstate 69, this home provides easy access to all the amenities you need. This home combines modern upgrades with thoughtful design, making it a perfect place to create cherished memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
